Libraries used:
- **RF24**: This project utilizes the [RF24 Arduino library](https://github.com/nRF24/RF24) for managing the nRF24L01 wireless modules. Please check the RF24 repository for its specific license terms.

Note: The **Library** folder in this repository contains the RF24 library for users' convenience.
